{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "vacayplan-a2-collection",
    "name": "VacayPlan A2 - Full API Collection",
    "description": "IFQ636 Assignment 2 — full API test collection covering auth, admin, trips, activities and weather endpoints.\n\nFolders:\n- Auth (Rodney #89)\n- Admin / CoR (Rodney #89)\n- Trips + State (Lance #90)\n- Activities + Weather (Joe #91)\n\nRun requests in folder order. Login runs first to populate {{token}}; Create Trip populates {{tripId}}; Create Activity populates {{activityId}}.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Auth (Rodney #89)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Register - happy path (201)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
                  "    const json = pm.response.json();",
                  "    if (json.token) pm.environment.set('token', json.token);",
                  "    pm.test('Status 201', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "    pm.test('Token returned', () => pm.expect(json.token).to.be.a('string'));",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"name\": \"Test User\",\n  \"email\": \"postman-test@delete.me\",\n  \"password\": \"Test1234!\"\n}",
              "options": { "raw": { "language": "json" } }
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"],
              "path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
            }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Register - missing fields (400)",
          "request": {
